<div class="tldr-box">
  <h3>TL;DR, Our pick for Indians</h3>
  <p><strong>For most Indian users in 2026: Claude.</strong> Better at long-form Indian English, doesn't fumble on Hinglish, has cleaner pricing for INR users, and the free tier is genuinely useful for daily work.</p>
  <p><strong>Pick ChatGPT instead if:</strong> you need image generation built-in, voice mode, or the broader plugin/GPT ecosystem for very specific workflows.</p>
