<p>If you've spent any time on Indian tech Twitter or LinkedIn in 2026, you've seen this debate. Two AI tools dominate the conversation: <strong>ChatGPT</strong> from OpenAI, and <strong>Claude</strong> from Anthropic. Both have free tiers. Both have ₹1,700+/month paid plans. Both work from India.</p>

<p>The question isn't "which is better in general." It's "which is better <em>for an Indian</em> who pays in rupees, deals with GST, sometimes writes in Hinglish, and doesn't want to fight a payment gateway every month?"</p>

<p>I've used both daily for the past year from India. Here's the honest comparison.</p>

<h2>Pricing in INR (the real cost, with GST)</h2>

<p>Both tools list prices in USD on their global pages. Here's what you'll actually pay from India in 2026:</p>

